(c) forming a first interconnection metal film having copper as a main component over the first barrier metal film both outside and inside the first interconnection region so as to fill the first interconnection region; 
(d) removing both the first interconnection metal film and the first barrier metal film outside the first interconnection region by chemical mechanical polishing; and thereafter 
(e) performing PVA brush scrub cleaning of the first main surface with liquid; and thereafter 
(f) making the first main surface dry; and thereafter 
(g) performing ammonia plasma treatment of the first main surface so as to reduce and nitride upper surfaces of both the first interlayer insulating film and the first interconnection metal film; and thereafter 
(h) forming a copper diffusion barrier insulating film over the first main surface, 
wherein steps (g) and (h) are performed without exposing the wafer to atmosphere.
